OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOldham cafe owner fined for
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fusing neighbour's bins     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A cafe owner who dumped his rubbish    
OL,6, into other people's bins has been      
OL,7, ordered to pay out more than #4,000.   
OL,9,FDavid Herbert, who runs Arizona Cafe in
OL,10,FOldham, sneaked the waste in his       
OL,11,Fnext-door neighbour's bins.            
OL,13,FThe council found he had not paid to   
OL,14,Fhave his own rubbish collected and     
OL,15,Fneighbours also complained.            
OL,17,FThe 56-year-old was arrested after     
OL,18,Ffailing to appear at court and has now 
OL,19,Fbeen fined #1,200 and ordered to pay   
OL,20,F#2,960 costs.                          
